{{Quote|Rumor has it the Leo Bellsfar named the ''Rusted Cutlass II'' in honor of the original ''Rusted Cutlass''.|[[Platt Okeefe/Legends|Platt Okeefe]]|<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>}}
The '''''Rusted Cutlass II''''' was a bulbous [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]] that belonged to the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]] which was attached to [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']]. While most of their fleet was concealed in the [[Phosphura Belt Nebula/Legends|Phosphura Belt Nebula]], the pirates' [[Leo Bellsfar/Legends|leader]] at the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] resided at the ''Rusted Cutlass II''.<ref name="Zirtran's Anchor" />

